<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Shopify → Andreani</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');
  :root {
    --bg: #0f0f0f; --surface: #161616; --surface2: #1e1e1e;
    --border: #2a2a2a; --accent: #00e5a0; --accent-dim: rgba(0,229,160,0.12);
    --accent-glow: rgba(0,229,160,0.3); --text: #f0f0f0; --text-dim: #888;
    --text-muted: #555; --danger: #ff4d6d;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  
  header {
    background: var(--surface); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 32px; height: 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
  .logo-icon { width: 28px; height: 28px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 14px; }
  .logo span { color: var(--accent); }

  main { flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 40px 24px; }

  .card {
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 48px 40px; max-width: 440px; width: 100%; text-align: center;
  }
  .card-icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .card h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .card p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 32px; }

  .form-field { margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: left; }
  label { display: block; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  input {
    width: 100%; background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 14px; color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: none;
    transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
  }
  input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-dim); }
  input::placeholder { color: var(--text-muted); }

  .btn-primary {
    width: 100%; padding: 13px; background: var(--accent); color: #000;
    border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: all .2s;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #00ffb2; box-shadow: 0 0 24px var(--accent-glow); }

  .features { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 32px; text-align: left; }
  .feature { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dim); }
  .feature-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .error-msg {
    background: rgba(255,77,109,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,77,109,0.3);
    color: var(--danger); border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .already-auth {
    background: var(--accent-dim); border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,160,0.3);
    color: var(--accent); border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .already-auth a { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="logo">
    <div class="logo-icon">📦</div>
    Shopify <span>→</span> Andreani
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-icon">🚚</div>
    <h1>Exportar pedidos a Andreani</h1>
    <p>Conectá tu tienda Shopify y generá el CSV listo para importar en Andreani en segundos.</p>

    <% if (authenticated) { %>
    <div class="already-auth">
      ✓ Ya conectada con <strong><%= shop %></strong> — <a href="/orders">Ver pedidos →</a>
    </div>
    <% } %>

    <% if (locals.error) { %>
    <div class="error-msg">⚠ Error al conectar. Verificá el dominio e intentá de nuevo.</div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature"><div class="feature-dot"></div>Sin configuración — conectás con un clic</div>
      <div class="feature"><div class="feature-dot"></div>Tus datos nunca se almacenan en ningún servidor</div>
      <div class="feature"><div class="feature-dot"></div>CSV en el formato exacto de Andreani</div>
    </div>

    <form method="POST" action="/auth">
      <div class="form-field">
        <label>Dominio de tu tienda Shopify</label>
        <input type="text" name="shop" placeholder="mi-tienda.myshopify.com" required />
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">
        🔐 Conectar con Shopify
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</main>
</body>
</html>
